65
00:03:23,500 --> 00:03:25,760
还在研究法典?
Still working on the Codex?

66
00:03:25,830 --> 00:03:27,900
我不想让自己胡思乱想
I'm trying to keep my mind occupied.

67
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,230
不管用的
And it's not working.

68
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:31,660
Siegel总是浮现在我的脑海
