00:40:32,640 --> 00:40:34,680
好运
Good luck.

901
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:46,840
看来他感觉好多了
Seems like he's feeling better.

902
00:40:46,910 --> 00:40:49,640
是啊 你呢?
Yeah. How about you?

903
00:40:49,710 --> 00:40:51,180
再次结案的感觉如何?
How does it feel to close a case again?

904
00:40:51,240 --> 00:40:54,640
我不确定是否算结案
I'm not so sure the case is closed.

905
00:40:54,710 --> 00:40:59,040
Summers终于肯松口告诉我们她把200万藏哪里了
Summers cracked and told us where she hid the $2 million,

906
00:40:59,110 --> 00:41:03,210
但我们去找的时候却没找到
but when we went to retrieve it, it wasn't there.

907
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:05,980
至少我们弄到了她的招供
Hmm, good thing we got a confession.

908
00:41:21,980 --> 00:41:23,880
你是说这个归我了?
You're telling me I can have this?

909
00:41:23,940 --> 00:41:25,980
把它当作我那天晚上
Consider it an apology

910
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:27,580
对你说的话的道歉吧
for all the things I said the other night.

911
00:41:27,640 --> 00:41:29,210
忠言逆耳而已
They were things I needed to hear.

912
00:41:29,280 --> 00:41:32,540
是时候重建帝国了 老朋友
It's time to rebuild the empire, my friend.

913
00:41:32,610 --> 00:41:34,780
友情提醒 钞票做了标记
Word of caution. The bills are marked.

914
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:37,440
每一美元我还是可以换来50美分的 仍是一笔不错的收获
I can get 50 cents on the dollar. Still a pretty good haul.

915
00:41:37,510 --> 00:41:39,880
我还以为小菜一碟呢
I figured it wouldn't be a problem.

916
00:41:39,950 --> 00:41:42,720
这是从你自己直系猫咪探长
This is illegally obtained contraband from one

917
00:41:42,790 --> 00:41:46,390
手上的案子里非法搞来的
of your very own suit's Federal investigations.

918
00:41:46,450 --> 00:41:49,290
你为什么要拿?
So why'd you take it?

919
00:41:49,350 --> 00:41:52,490
因为它就在那儿
Because it was there.

920
00:41:52,550 --> 00:41:54,620
总有一天我要找到合适的说法
One day I'll find the right words,

921
00:41:54,690 --> 00:41:56,120
一定要言简意赅
and they will be simple.

922
00:41:56,190 --> 00:41:57,850
- 凯鲁亚克说的  - 没错
- Kerouac.  - Yeah.

923
00:41:57,920 --> 00:41:59,290
不能更言简意赅了
Can't get much simpler than that.

924
00:41:59,350 --> 00:42:01,190
对于咱们这样的来说就不是了
Not for guys like us.

925
00:42:01,250 --> 00:42:05,850
咱们这样的? 你要回归老日子了?
Guys like us? You coming back to the life?

926
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:09,450
那你第一步如何打算?
So what's your first plan of action?

927
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:11,120
改变战局
Change the state of play.

928
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:13,550
我有太多主子了
I've been serving too many masters.

929
00:42:13,620 --> 00:42:14,790
我受够了当每个人的玩偶
I'm through being everyone's puppet.

930
00:42:14,850 --> 00:42:17,890
Hagen 联邦调查局...
Hagen, the FBI...

931
00:42:17,950 --> 00:42:20,450
你到底计划脱离哪一方呢?
Which strings, exactly, do you plan on cutting?

932
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:22,230
一旦时机成熟...
When the time comes...

933
00:42:23,170 --> 00:42:24,170
统统再见
all of them.

